des:
The Heatzy Wizard allows you to simply change the operating mode of all your Heatzy products with a simple voice command.

Use the following steps to controls your devices by this skill
1. Download Amazon "Alexa" app and "Heatzy" app ;
2. Register an account in "Alexa" app and "Heatzy" app;
3. Add your device and set the device name in "Heatzy" app;
4. Search "Heatzy" skill from the "Alexa" app;
5. Select the "Enable Skill" button in the "Alexa" App;
6. Enter your Heatzy account user name and password login

Your devices now talk directly to the Amazon Echo through Alexa. You can control your devices with simple statements like:
- Alexa, set Heatzy to eco
- Alexa, set Heatzy to heat
- Alexa, set Heatzy to auto
- Alexa, set Heatzy to cool
- Alexa, turn off Heatzy

if you have any questions, feel free to contact us by email at contact@heatzy.com.
